channel.title: Live: NASCAR Xfinity Racing Series
channel.desc: The NASCAR Xfinity Series returns to Daytona for the Wawa 250. Connor Zilisch took his fourth checkered flag in five races Aug. 9 at Watkins Glen, but an unfortunate tumble during the celebration led to a broken collarbone for the 19-year-old rookie.
